l <- read.csv("Dataset1-Media-Example-EDGES.csv", header=T, as.is=T)
l <- aggregate(l[,3], l[,-3], sum)
l <- l[order(l$from, l$to),]
colnames(l)[4] <- "weight"
rownames(l) <- NULL
net <- graph_from_data_frame(d=l, vertices=n, directed=T)
